description:
Newly engaged Property Brother Drew Scott and his fiance Linda hunt for their first home together in Los Angeles before their wedding day! It's a family affair from beginning to end as Drew finds the home, Jonathan designs it and Linda oversees the decorating.



Property Brothers at Home - Season 3, Episode 1 (Drew's Honeymoon House)



Living Room Luxury

Drew and his fiance Linda are having a huge year -- they are newly engaged, planning their wedding and have just bought a vintage fixer-upper in Los Angeles. Tackling their most personal and largest project ever, Drew and Jonathan have just 12 weeks to renovate the outdated house into the family home of their dreams. They begin transforming the home from tired to luxurious with projects in the entrance, powder room, office and living room.



Original Air Date: 22-Nov-2017
